{"tid":2134214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★海關檢獲逾1.3萬個含菌量超標外科口罩 西環、旺角及九龍灣藥房有售","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:05:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40f20bf30c17eb1ec3a9ee7137a6ced9f65cf9db","tid":2134214,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2710000/2711705/116015911_1007968626309380_7664666272918706495_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2710000%2F2711705%2F116015911_1007968626309380_7664666272918706495_n_1024.jpg&h=a4474b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關昨日（30日）檢獲434盒逾1.3萬個懷疑含菌量超出標準上限，涉嫌違反《消費品安全條例》的外科口罩，呼籲市民馬上停用；商戶如有出售，亦應立即下架。<br />\n<br />\n海關接獲最新一批14個由試購所得，外科口罩樣本的化驗報告。根據相關一次性使用衞生用品衞生標準，顯示其中一款樣本的細菌菌落總數超出標準上限1.3倍，涉嫌違法。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>涉事外科口罩30片盒裝，每片口罩均有獨立包裝，產品包裝上標示的產地為中國</strong></span>，是海關於7月初的試購行動中，在西環一間藥房購得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2711705/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2q6eH-4_Umx2O3VyB-Uz11fE0MCL7xtZ2zB2EreRM4Lg-4yfnntN4jcXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2711705%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb%26fbclid%3DIwAR2q6eH-4_Umx2O3VyB-Uz11fE0MCL7xtZ2zB2EreRM4Lg-4yfnntN4jcXw&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=5385a8a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2711705/?r=mcsdfb&amp;fbclid=IwAR2q6eH-4_Umx2O3VyB-Uz11fE0MCL7xtZ2zB2EreRM4Lg-4yfnntN4jcXw</a><br />\n<br />\n海關：口罩由內地進口<br />\n<br />\n經調查後，海關昨日在一間位於葵涌的供應商辦公室檢獲304盒同款口罩。調查顯示，涉案外科口罩由該供應商從內地進口，供應予本地3間分別位於西環、旺角及九龍灣的藥房。同日，海關再於3間藥房檢獲共130盒該款口罩，售價為98元至128元不等。<br />\n<br />\n]行動中，海關共拘捕4名年齡介乎41至77歲涉案人士，包括一名供應商董事、一名藥房董事及兩名藥房東主，目前正保釋候查。海關將就涉案口罩作進一步化驗，以確定含菌種類。<br />\n<br />\n除搜查涉案的藥房外，人員亦同時巡查全港多個零售點，暫未再發現有該款外科口罩出售。"},{"pid":"4d692a5a16345c4160b5a805f64a348adf20ee40","tid":2134214,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a057e486f3efd4c85a930bae87f596e52158291","tid":2134214,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"產地為中國仲要藥房買嗰個都白痴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770b19bb76cdc814edfb1ad066a1bb1bfcd79f19","tid":2134214,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"mask crab?"}]}